<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bù zhī dào qián fāng de lù hái yǒu duō yuǎn 迦南93</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bù zhī dào qián fāng de lù hái yǒu duō yuǎn,
 bù zhī dào yǒu duō shǎo jiān nán hé wēi xiǎn,
 dàn wǒ men de xīn yuàn yǐ dìng bù zài gǎi biàn,
 kāi gōng méi yǒu huí tóu jiàn, méi yǒu huí tóu jiàn,
 lái ba ràng wǒ men qí xīn hé lì, chōng guò jī liú xiǎn tān,
 bù yào pà nà dào lù nán zǒu qū zhé wān yán,
 wǒ men yào fù chū xuè de dài jià. jiāng fú yīn zhǒng zi sā biàn,
 bù qiú de shàng de bào chóu zhǐ qiú tiān shàng lái jì niàn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
</song>